- `homework-2`: support-ticket API with CSV/JSON/XML import, rule-based classification, >85% coverage, multi-level docs, fixtures, performance checks, and diagrams.
- `homework-3`: documentation-only finance spec package. No implementation code unless the user changes scope.
- `homework-4`: four-agent bug/security/test pipeline with explicit model choices, skills, result reports, one-command execution, seeded app issues, and screenshots.
- `homework-5`: configure GitHub, filesystem, Jira/Notion, and custom FastMCP servers; include working MCP screenshots and reproducible setup docs.
- `homework-6`: capstone multi-agent banking pipeline with spec-first workflow, file-based JSON agent communication, context7 research notes, FastMCP status server, skills, coverage hook, tests, docs, and screenshots.
